* George Brown College's Centre for Hospitality and Culinary Arts is located in downtown Toronto.
* Open House Discovery Days are offered both in-person and online.
* Interested individuals can register for In-Person Open House Discovery Days or Online Open House Discovery Day.

* Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
